wiki.content:
One Last Breath from Creed appeared first on the Weathered album. It's about wanting to cry for help but not having the energy to shout for help or to show you're in trouble. The problems described in the song seem to be influenced by some love problems.
 The videoclip for this song can be found on YouTube. Yeah Boy!!!!!  Dad's a boy.
